Centennial.Stonegate, Colorado:
Stonegate is an unincorporated community and census-designated place (CDP) in Douglas County, Colorado, United States. The population was 8,962 at the 2010 census, up from 6,284 at the 2000 census.


== Geography ==
Stonegate is located in northeastern Douglas County at 39°31′54″N 104°48′6″W (39.531581, -104.801657).
